#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:227
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM\"]/title"
msgstr "Shipvore Ram"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:228
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) Their signature combat augment lets you repeatedly ram the enemy for guaranteed quickly lethal damage, free repairs and sometimes other things. WARNING: your ship and/or crew may suffer. [Uses {, Full Power uses more and destroys the augment. Emergency Generator and Fuel Conserver can apply.]\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be reinforced at empty beacons to survive the next Full Power use."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:246
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"LOCKED_DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM\"]/title"
msgstr "Shipvore Ram"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:247
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"LOCKED_DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) Their signature combat augment lets you repeatedly ram the enemy for guaranteed quickly lethal damage, free repairs and sometimes other things. WARNING: your ship and/or crew may suffer. [Uses {, Full Power uses more. Emergency Generator and Fuel Conserver can apply.]\n"
"\t\n"
"\tThe ship was built around this locked version that survives Full Power use. Also gives 9% faster shield recharge and chance to ignore hull damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:266
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_OFF\"]/title"
msgstr "Charged Belts (Off)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:267
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_OFF\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) This augment is Off but can be toggled On anytime. When On:\n"
"\n"
"\t[This double-edged augment equips your crew with belts that [style[color:ff3377]]reduce their HP by 10% (beware of Vagabonds)[[/style]] and explode when they die, causing a fire and dealing damage to the room and ship they're in, with extra damage in systemless rooms. [style[color:ff3377]]Has friendly fire.[[/style]]\n"
"\tStacks upon already existing death effects.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t[style[color:ff3377]]WARNING: Can't be toggled Off.[[/style]] Can scrap itself into ~ or } at empty beacons.\n"
"\n"
"\tCOMBO: Makes any crew a fire source for Plasma Teleporter.]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:280
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_ON\"]/title"
msgstr "Charged Belts"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:281
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_ON\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) This double-edged augment equips your crew with belts that [style[color:ff3377]]reduce their HP by 10% (beware of Vagabonds)[[/style]] and explode when they die, causing a fire and dealing damage to the room and ship they're in, with extra damage in systemless rooms. [style[color:ff3377]]Has friendly fire.[[/style]]\n"
"\tStacks upon already existing death effects.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t[style[color:ff3377]]WARNING: Can't be toggled Off.[[/style]] Can scrap itself into ~ or } at empty beacons.\n"
"\n"
"\tCOMBO: Makes any crew a fire source for Plasma Teleporter."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:294
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_AUTO_SYS_REPAIR\"]/title"
msgstr "A.E.R.A. Second Wind"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:295
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_AUTO_SYS_REPAIR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) 'Automated Emergency Repair Augment'.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tWhen you activate this Combat augment, if your ship is almost destroyed during the fight (9 Hull or less), a nanomachine burst is triggered, fully repairing your systems and 15 Hull points. [Activation uses 1 power, Emergency Generator can apply]\n"
"\t\t[style[color:ff3377]]The effect also destroys the augment. No effect if your hull instantly reaches 0.[[/style]]\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tYou can also trigger this via the Toggle Menu anytime for 1{."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:308
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_LEAD_TITANS\"]/title"
msgstr "Lead Titans"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:309
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_LEAD_TITANS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) Someone had the insane idea to weave motile fiber-lead into muscles. \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tYour 'big' crew (Crystals, Lanius, Rockmen, Saltmen) have: 2.5x resistance to everything, deal 2.5x damage to everything.\n"
"\t\t[style[color:ff3377]]The weight makes them take 2 crew slots, create breaches while walking, and they can't repair.[[/style]]\n"
"\t\tYour other crew get a flat +75% repair speed from smaller fibers.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tAll your crew gain a flat +40% movement speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\t[style[color:ff3377]]WARNING: Can't be toggled Off.[[/style]] Can scrap itself at empty beacons."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:324
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_BAM_DIVINE_ARMOR\"]/title"
msgstr "Thicker Hull"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:325
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_BAM_DIVINE_ARMOR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) RadiKals reverse engineered very rare armor from captured Theocracy inquisitors into this slightly more accessible and less perfect armor.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tReduces weapon charge speed by 5%.\n"
"\t\tImpacts that deal 1 damage have a 40% chance to be negated, and all other damage is reduced by 1."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:337
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_PERSISTENCE_SHIELD\"]/title"
msgstr "Persistence Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:338
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_PERSISTENCE_SHIELD\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) A staple of high-end ships relying on shields, made possible by stress tests on many Zoltan scouts who never came home.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tAdds a 4 hitpoints Super Shield. Stacks with other super shields, but not with itself.\n"
"\t\tAlso increases shield charge speed by 20%.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tActivate from the Toggle Menu to instantly restore all your Supershield layers. [Uses 1 {]\n"
"\t\tCannot be activated again until you rebuild its capacitor at an empty beacon for 7~ ."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:390
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_ARROGANCE_SHIELD\"]/title"
msgstr "Arrogance Shield"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:391
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_ARROGANCE_SHIELD\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) Risky for your Shields but could make you untouchable. Strange cubes died for this.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tAdds a 9 hitpoints Super Shield. Stacks with other Super Shields, but not with itself.\n"
"\t\tOn your ship, your crew-drones also gain 3 HP/second while enemy crew-drones lose that much.\n"
"\t\t[style[color:ff3377]]WARNING: Reduces Shield charge speed by 25% and Weapons charge speed by 5%.[[/style]]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:402
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_DEFENSE_REMOVER\"]/title"
msgstr "Vulnerabilizer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:403
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_DEFENSE_REMOVER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) This combat augment slowly weakens the enemy's defenses. Bosses hate it.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tEvery 3 to 7 seconds (at random), limits enemy Shields and Engines by 1 power. This effect stacks up to 16 times if lucky.\n"
"\t\tAll effects end after 40 to 75 seconds, based on how many drones you choose to use.\n"
"\t\t[Uses 1-2 | and 3 reactor power. Emergency Generator can apply.]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:415
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_OFFENSE_DISABLER\"]/title"
msgstr "Offense Disabler"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:416
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_OFFENSE_DISABLER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) This combat augment can fully disable enemy offense for 6 seconds. Then, the effect becomes weaker until it's gone at 18 seconds (you will be warned). Perfect against aggressive enemies!\n"
"\t\t[Uses 2| and 3 reactor power. Emergency Generator can apply.]\n"
"\n"
"\t\tAffected systems:\n"
"\t\tWeapons, Drone Control, Mind Control,\n"
"\t\tHacking, Teleporter, all Artilleries,\n"
"\t\tCorruptor (from \"Darkest Desire\"),\n"
"\t\tand Turrets (from \"The Old Guard\")."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:444
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_HACK_FLEET\"]/title"
msgstr "Enigmashin"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:445
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_HACK_FLEET\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) This combat augment attempts to send deepfake intel to the rebels through an enemy's comms for credibility. Success delays the fleet, Crit-fail accelerates it.\n"
"\t\tIf you deal more than 2 hull damage during the process, it stops. \n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tFree use takes 17 seconds. Limit your Hacking system and use droneparts for faster, better results. (Someone might notice)\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tChances (Good / Crit / Crit-fail)\n"
"\t\t0| no hacking = 60% / 5% / 15%\n"
"\t\t1| hacking 1 = 70% / 10% / 10%\n"
"\t\t2| hacking 2 = 80% / 15% / 5% / +???\n"
"\t\t3| hacking 3 = 90% / 30% / 5% / +???"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:461
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_DREAD_DECK\"]/title"
msgstr "Dread Deck"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:462
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_DREAD_DECK\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) Doesn't directly do anything, but seasoned crew start praying and social distancing whenever this augment shows up.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tEnemies aboard your ship take 1.7x damage from everything.\n"
"\t\tYour crew have 2x cloning speed and healing from most sources. They lose no skills from cloning.\n"
"\t\tAll crew in the same room as any of your crew cannot be cloned."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:473
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SUPER_DEFENDERS\"]/title"
msgstr "Defense Kits"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:474
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SUPER_DEFENDERS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) With all the risks they take, sometimes RadiKals need extra survivability. These kits include light motorized armor for all shapes and sizes, drugs, and other medical equipment.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tOn your ship, your crew have 0.75x damage taken, 1.3x repair speed, 1.3x movement speed, and a 4 HP/second heal while idle (not even manning)."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:484
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_OWN_HARMONY_ON\"]/title"
msgstr "Punk Harmony"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:485
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_OWN_HARMONY_ON\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) Some daft RadiKal Punks made their own Harmony. [style[color:ff3377]]Controls your Engis[[/style]] on your ship, giving them immunity to (further) mind control and +40% resistance to damage and stun. Powered levels in Hacking or Mind Control add 5/10/20/40/80/160% combat damage, repair speed, and movement speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tIn short, makes them harder, better, faster, stronger, and automated.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be toggled off anytime.\n"
"\n"
"\tAt empty beacons, you can grow a Separatist for 15~, 1{ and 1|, but [style[color:ff3377]]the rebel fleet accelerates for 1 turn[[/style]]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:497
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_OWN_HARMONY_OFF\"]/title"
msgstr "Punk Harmony (OFF)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:498
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_OWN_HARMONY_OFF\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) Some daft RadiKal Punks made their own Harmony. [style[color:ff3377]]Controls your Engis[[/style]] on your ship, giving them immunity to (further) mind control and +40% resistance to damage and stun. Powered levels in Hacking or Mind Control add 5/10/20/40/80/160% combat damage, repair speed, and movement speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tIn short, makes them harder, better, faster, stronger, and automated.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be toggled on anytime.\n"
"\n"
"\tAt empty beacons, you can grow a Separatist for 15~, 1{ and 1|, but [style[color:ff3377]]the rebel fleet accelerates for 1 turn[[/style]]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:525
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FIRE_IMMUNITY\"]/title"
msgstr "Fire Immunity"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:526
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"FIRE_IMMUNITY\"]/desc"
msgstr "Systems take 100% less fire damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:537
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SCORCH_SELF\"]/title"
msgstr "Scorched Earth (T1)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:538
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SCORCH_SELF\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Scorch gear) Your crew take 0.6x fire damage and get 3x extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second, +2 per powered level in O2.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tActivate from the Toggles menu to set any system room on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCOMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be upgraded twice at empty beacons, increasing the fire resistances and gaining an effect."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:554
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SCORCH_SELF_2\"]/title"
msgstr "Blazing Earth (T2)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:555
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SCORCH_SELF_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Scorch gear) [Tier 2 Scorched Earth] Your crew take 0.45x fire damage and get 3x extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second, +2 per powered level in O2.\n"
"\t\tIn fire, they also produce O2 like 1 Orchid.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tActivate from the Toggles menu to set any system room on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCOMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be upgraded once at empty beacons, increasing the fire resistances and O2 production."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:573
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SCORCH_SELF_3\"]/title"
msgstr "Erupting Earth (T3)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:574
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SCORCH_SELF_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Scorch gear) [Tier 3 Scorched Earth] Your crew take 0.3x fire damage and get 3x extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second, +2 per powered level in O2.\n"
"\t\tIn fire, they also produce O2 like 3 Orchids.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tActivate from the Toggles menu to set any system room on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCOMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:589
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_SCORCH_ENEMY\"]/title"
msgstr "Plasma Teleporter"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:590
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_SCORCH_ENEMY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Scorch gear) This combat augment can set the enemy ship on fire at start of combat, outright winning some fights.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tNeeds a fire source: 1} (weak effect),\n"
"\t\tor: Uptor/Goul/Lost Sun/Shell/Zoltan ([style[color:ff3377]]they die[[/style]], can be cloned, strong effect).\n"
"\t\tUsing a Ghost has an extra effect.\n"
"\t\t[Uses 1{, [style[color:ff3377]]ignites your O2 system[[/style]].]\n"
"\n"
"\tCOMBO: Charged Belts / Martyr Vests make all crew fire sources.\n"
"\tCOMBO: any Scorched Earth removes the need for a fire source."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:605
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_ENEMIES_CAN_BURN\"]/title"
msgstr "Flammabilizer-Immune"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:606
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_ENEMIES_CAN_BURN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Scorch gear) Passively removes the fire immunity of enemies, and limits their fire resistance to 0%. Enemies who invert fire damage stop doing that. Vulnerable enemies (like Orchids) are unaffected.\n"
"\tWorks on both ships.\n"
"\n"
"\tCan be toggled anytime to make non-fireproof enemies take more fire damage instead.\n"
"\tBoth toggle modes make enemies move 20% slower in fire (up to 80% with 3 power in O2)."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:617
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_ENEMIES_BURN_MORE\"]/title"
msgstr "Flammabilizer-Damage"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:618
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_ENEMIES_BURN_MORE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Scorch gear) Passively makes enemies who can burn take 75% more fire damage, scaling up to 375% with 4 power in your Life Support (O2) system.\n"
"\tWorks on both ships.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be toggled anytime to make fireproof and fire-resistant enemies vulnerable to fire instead.\n"
"\tBoth toggle modes make enemies move 20% slower in fire (up to 80% with 3 power in O2)."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:630
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_OXYGENIZER\"]/title"
msgstr "Oxygenizer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:631
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_OXYGENIZER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Scorch combat augment can basically shoot out giant canisters of ultracompressed O2 to fill the void of space when a fight starts.\n"
"\tPuts both ships in an atmosphere, making breaches and open vents fill oxygen instead of depleting it. Shenanigans ensue. [Uses 2}]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:640
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SCORCH_PREIGNITER\"]/title"
msgstr "Scorch Pre-Igniter"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:641
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SCORCH_PREIGNITER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Scorch gear) Weapons are made immediately available after an FTL jump but they light a fire in the Weapons room every time they shoot a projectile or beam.\n"
"\t\tThis variant of the famous Weapon Pre-igniter is flawed but more accessible.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tCOMBO: Increases Weapons On Fire's max extra bonus to 20%"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:652
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_WEAPONS_ON_FIRE\"]/title"
msgstr "Weapons On Fire"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:653
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_WEAPONS_ON_FIRE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Scorch gear) The fire rate of your Weapons and Artilleries is improved by 25%.\n"
"\t\tGain an extra 1% fire rate every time they shoot a projectile or beam (up to 10%), but at the same time there's a 10% chance to light a fire in the Weapon Control and any Artillery rooms.\n"
"\t\tThe extra bonus is reset on jump.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tCOMBO: Scorch Preigniter increases max extra bonus to 20%"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:664
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_WEAPONS_ON_FIRE_TEMP\"]/title"
msgstr "Weapons On Fire"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:665
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_WEAPONS_ON_FIRE_TEMP\"]/desc"
msgstr "YOU SHOULD NEVER SEE THIS 1% weapon fire rate."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:683
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_BPS_SURVEYOR\"]/title"
msgstr "RK Surveyor"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:684
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_BPS_SURVEYOR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(BPS gear) The ingenuity of RadiKals from all subfactions lets you deep-search most empty beacons, at a non-negligible cost.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tYou can choose to retrieve/steal the random weapon or augment found, accelerating the fleet 1 turn."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:694
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_BPS_SHIELD_OVER_MATTER\"]/title"
msgstr "Shield Over Matter"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:695
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_BPS_SHIELD_OVER_MATTER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK BPS gear) Provides an Energy Shield with an integrity of 10 hitpoints. (Does not stack with itself or other non-stacking Energy Shields)\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tWhenever you take hull damage, it has a 50% chance to restore 1 layer of Energy Shields but when that happens, [style[color:ff3377]]the room that was hit catches fire (on top of any fire chance from the weapon that did the damage)[[/style]]."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:723
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_ACE_CONSOLE\"]/title"
msgstr "Hacker Ace's Console"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:724
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_ACE_CONSOLE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) Secretly developed for the Rebellion who deny its existence, H.A.C. can do 2 things when a fight starts:\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tLimit enemy Engines, Shields, and Weapons by 1 for the whole fight [Free],\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tOr limit enemy Shields by 3, Engines and Weapons by 2, and Cloaking, Corruptor (from \"Darkest Desire\"), Drone Control, Mind Control, Oxygen, Piloting and Turret Controls (from \"The Old Guard\") by 1 for the whole fight. [Uses 3| and 2 reactor power. Emergency Generator can apply.]\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\tYou looted this from a MFK Hacker Ace."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:743
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\"]/title"
msgstr "Z. Police Warrant"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:744
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"RKS_POLICE_WARRANT\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltan Police foothold in the RadiKal Sector gave you this authorization to shake down suspicious passerbys for their RK gear. You could also sell it.\n"
"\t[Provides blue options in some beacons of the RadiKal Sector.]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:761
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"SHIP_RK\"]/title"
msgstr "RadiKal Cruiser"

