#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:875
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_RK_CALIBRATOR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) Your weapons have +10% accuracy and 4% increased fire rate. "
"Can be installed twice."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:882
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_RK_CHOKING_IS_FINE\"]/title"
msgstr "[X] Choking F.I.N.E."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:883
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_RK_CHOKING_IS_FINE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) Outlawed in many places like most of RK gear, the \"Choking Fetish-Inducing Neural Entrancers\" are often in-demand.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tYour crew take 0.75x suffocation damage.\n"
"\t\tWhile suffocating, they move, sabotage, repair and fight 1.5x better.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t[X] - As an external system upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. Can be converted for free to the internal version under the internal upgrade menu.\n"
"\tDoes not stack with itself, but stacks with the internal version..."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:895
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_RK_CHOKING_IS_FINE\"]/title"
msgstr "Choking F.I.N.E."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:896
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_RK_CHOKING_IS_FINE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) Outlawed in many places like most of RK gear, the \"Choking Fetish-Inducing Neural Entrancers\" are often in-demand.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tYour crew take 0.75x suffocation damage.\n"
"\t\tWhile suffocating, they move, sabotage, repair and fight 1.5x better."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:906
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\"]/title"
msgstr "Demicloners"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:907
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) These backpack-clonebay prototypes are infused with dark energies. They try to resurrect your crew if they die (not in events) when you don't have a real Clonebay.\n"
"\t\tAt best, crew resurrect as their own lesser version (Soldier = default Human, etc.) If no lesser version exists, they become Morphs. When Morphs die, nothing happens."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:915
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\"]/title"
msgstr "[X] Demicloners"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:916
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The RadiKal Punk infused these backpack-clonebay prototypes with dark energies. These try to resurrect your crew if they die (not in events) when you don't have a real Clonebay.\n"
"\t\tAt best, crew resurrect as their own lesser version (Soldier = default Human, etc.) If no lesser version exists, they become Morphs. When Morphs die, nothing happens.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t[X] - As an external system upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. Can be converted for free to the internal version under the internal upgrade menu.\n"
"\tDoes not stack with itself, but stacks with the internal version..."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:928
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_MC_PARALYZER\"]/title"
msgstr "Mind Cooler"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:929
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_MC_PARALYZER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"When under the effects of Mind Control, your crew cannot fight, sabotage, or"
" teleport away. Works on both ships."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:937
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_RK_IN_FIRE_CREWBOOSTS\"]/title"
msgstr "Hellion Wraps"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:938
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_RK_IN_FIRE_CREWBOOSTS\"]/desc"
msgstr "2x crew speed and damage in fire on both ships."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:946
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_MC_IMMUNE_FROM_FIRE\"]/title"
msgstr "Mind Heater"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:947
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_MC_IMMUNE_FROM_FIRE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"In fire, your crew are immune to Mind Control and cured from it, stunned 50%"
" shorter, and reveal adjacent rooms. Works on both ships."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1000
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_BAM_CREW\"]/title"
msgstr "Boon of the RK Bam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1001
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_BAM_CREW\"]/desc"
msgstr "RadiKals gain 29 more health and 1.1x combat damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1007
