"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_PUNK_CREW\"]/desc"
msgstr "RadiKals heal and are cloned 40% faster."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1014
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_SCORCH_CREW\"]/title"
msgstr "Boon of the RK Scorch"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1015
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_SCORCH_CREW\"]/desc"
msgstr "In fire, RadiKals gain 1.3x movement speed and combat damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1074
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_BAM_EQUIPMENT\"]/title"
msgstr "Blessing of RadiKal Toughness"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1075
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_BAM_EQUIPMENT\"]/desc"
msgstr "+8% chance to resist hull, system and ion damage from enemy weapons."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1082
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_PUNK_EQUIPMENT\"]/title"
msgstr "Blessing of RadiKal Cunning"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1083
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_PUNK_EQUIPMENT\"]/desc"
msgstr "Your systems are repaired at x1.3 speed."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1089
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_SCORCH_EQUIPMENT\"]/title"
msgstr "Blessing of RadiKal Fever"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1090
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_SCORCH_EQUIPMENT\"]/desc"
msgstr "+8% weapon charge speed and evasion."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1096
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_BPS_EQUIPMENT\"]/title"
msgstr "Blessing of RadiKal Projects"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1097
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"JUDGE_BOON_RK_BPS_EQUIPMENT\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"+4% chance to resist hull, system and ion damage from enemy weapons, your "
"systems are repaired at 1.15x speed, +4% weapon charge speed and evasion."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1197
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/title"
msgstr "'Bada' Fissure Beam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1198
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/short"
msgstr "'Bada' Beam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1199
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) Can hit 3-5 tiles, hard enough to destroy systems or ships.\n"
"\t\tFissure Beams deal damage per tile rather than per room."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1251
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_HEAVY_POPPER_2\"]/title"
msgstr "Heavy Popper MK II"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1252
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_HEAVY_POPPER_2\"]/short"
msgstr "He. Pop II"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1253
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_HEAVY_POPPER_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) Enough strength to unshield most enemies, and/or hurt badly.\n"
"\t\t[style[color:ff3377]]Your systems have 3% chance to take 1 damage each shot![[/style]]\n"
"\t\tHeavy Poppers are inaccurate slower Heavy Lasers that pop 2 shields."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1352
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_UNLOADER\"]/title"
msgstr "'Unloader' of missiles"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1353
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_UNLOADER\"]/short"
msgstr "Unloader"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1354
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_UNLOADER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Bam gear) People ask \"Why all these pre-ignited Letos in a supercooling"
" rotary missile loader?\" and the Bam answer \"We got a great bulk "
"discount.\""

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1533
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_KILLALL_BEAM\"]/title"
msgstr "'Gravespred' Rad-Beam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1534
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_KILLALL_BEAM\"]/short"
msgstr "Gravespred"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1535
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_KILLALL_BEAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) This radiation Beam wants everyone dead. Deals +15 crew damage per chain. [Max 105 crew damage]\n"
"\t\tPierces 2 shields +1 per chain. [Max 6 pierce. Ignore the tooltip]\n"
"\t\tWARNING: Deals 15 damage to crew on your ship per chain! [Max 60]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1582
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_MISSLAUNCHER_2_BATTERY\"]/title"
msgstr "'Battery Artemis' Missiles"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1583
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_MISSLAUNCHER_2_BATTERY\"]/short"
msgstr "'B. Artemis.'"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1584
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_MISSLAUNCHER_2_BATTERY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) The classic Artemis improved to provide power, at the cost of"
" some performance."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1786
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_RAIN_OF_ION\"]/title"
msgstr "Rain of Ions"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1787
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_RAIN_OF_ION\"]/short"
msgstr "Rain Ions"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1790
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_RAIN_OF_ION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) This heavy duty shotgun fires an accelerated phase ion, a heavy ion, a fire ion, a normal ion, a stun ion, and a radion (from fastest to slowest) all at once. Chains cooldown up to 4 times.\n"
"\t\tMany weapons worth of blue options!"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1860
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SHOTPHASER\"]/title"
msgstr "Shotphaser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1861
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SHOTPHASER\"]/short"
msgstr "Shotphaser"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1864
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"RK_SHOTPHASER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"(RK Punk gear) This shotgun fires 3 greatly accelerated phase ions in a small radius, with a high chance to stun.\n"
"\t\tPhasers pierce shields, dealing ion damage for the first layer of shields, as well as additional damage to whatever system hit."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1928
msgid ""
